The paper deals with the identification of artificially generated scientific manuscripts, which involves natural language processing and network analysis. The most relevant sub-category is likely to be cs.DL (Digital Libraries), which deals with the organization, retrieval, and distribution of digital information. Other relevant sub-categories include cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.CY (Computers and Society), and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
